data.title: Northumbria Students' Union
data.text:
About Magazine Society

We're a bunch of students who love being creative– Whether it's photography, writing, modelling, design or anything else. If you also want to be creative and collaborate with artists around the city, check out our social media and join us at our weekly socials.

Along with social events where we host editorial shoots and "Arts and Crafts" sessions, we'll be working towards our very own magazine by the end of the year.

Shoot us a message on Instagram @northumbriamagsoc if you're interested! And for those already joining us, our membership is £5, which will get you involved with our weekly socials, industry guest speakers, special discounts, and more.

Committee

All of our clubs and societies are run by a committee.

A committee is a team of people that lead, organise and publicise a group within your Students’ Union.

It can be really rewarding as well as being a great way to gain experience and invaluable skills for your future career.
